				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Guide to soloing the luggald broodmother<a name="45129"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 9 04 11:35 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Well that is the ranger/druid way of doing the BM... but it is far easier/faster to:
<br />

<br />
1) Tag BM, run up and accross the bridge to the large area with the firepit.
<br />

<br />
2) IF no other toons are in the vacinity fighting, then Fade and wait for most mobs to wander away.  If folks are fighting then just keep on moving as the BM has a HUGE aggro radius and we don't want to kill innocents.
<br />

<br />
3)  Kite the BM around the firepit, highsun her clerics, when BM dead, Fade the aggro and then loot.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
